{
  "stem": "21978.6",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And they had a farm.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "His father had a farm in Kenya.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But Robert is my husband, was established already as an [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "It's plumber.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And he had a business.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And he was a very successful businessman.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And he had lots of friends.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I lived in Kenya eight years.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Annetta was in kibbutz in Israel.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I always thought that eventually, we will be able to bring her husband and the family and Annetta to Kenya.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But when I came to Kenya, that was during the Mau Mau time, the trouble with Mau Mau.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I had to sleep with a gun under my pillow.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My husband was in the, in the police at night.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And when my daughter was born, my first-- the child was now, me, my daughter-- when she was born, my husband wasn't there.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "A friend took me to hospital.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] And he couldn't even come to visit me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now, he wouldn't stay with me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He would have fainted at the birth, you know?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "At those days, it didn't happen.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But he couldn't even visit me straightaway, because his leg was in plaster.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "During exercises, something happened.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But he-- we were happy.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then our second child was born there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I lived happily in Kenya for eight years.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Oh, and during that time, even during the Mau Mau, I never was frightened.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "People were killed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We had problems.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We had, in the townships, somebody was killed.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we knew people who were killed by the Mau Mau.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But I was never frightened.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I was so happy to have my husband and my family, my children.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "That was a miracle for me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And his parents were very good to me.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
